y-earth-wind-fires-september-sustains" target="_blank" rel="noopener">NPR</a> )</p></blockquote><p>请务必与 Jonathan Miller 一起观看本周的<a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">商业硕士课程</a>，他是<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.millersamuel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Miller Samuel</a>的首席执行官，这是他于 1986 年共同创立的一家房地产评估和咨询公司。他是纽约州和康涅狄格州的州认证房地产评估师，擅长执行作为专家证人出庭作证，并拥有房地产顾问 (CRE) 和认证搬迁专业人士 (CRP) 称号。他的每周电子邮件<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.millersamuel.com/email-lists/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“住房笔记”</a>在评估和房地产经纪行业都被广泛阅读。米勒·塞缪尔 (Miller Samuel) 的研究和数据分析推动了许多全国房地产经纪出版物和战略计划的发展。</p><p></p><p> <strong>Is America&#39;s minimum wage becoming irrelevant?</strong><br /> <a href="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage.png" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-318908" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage.png" alt="" width="600" height="600" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage.png 1198w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage-300x300.png 300w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage-1024x1024.png 1024w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage-150x150.png 150w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage-768x768.png 768w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/minwage-250x250.png 250w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a><br /> Source: <a href="https://www.chartr.co/newsletters/2023-08-23" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chartr</a></p><p></p><p> <a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://mailchi.mp/005fb77d75b9/ritholtzreads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"><em>在此注册我们的只读邮件列表</em></a>。</p><p></p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://ritholtz.com/2023/09/10-labor-day-reads-5/">10 Labor Day Reads</a> appeared first on <a rel="nof