/29/michael-farris-homeschoolers-parents-rights-ziklag/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Washington Post</a> )</p><p> • <strong>He spread conspiracies about elections. Now he oversees them</strong> : A controversy over conspiracy theories that has engulfed a small Iowa county shows the continuing power of Donald Trump&#39;s false claims about election fraud. ( <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-66589065" target="_blank" rel="noopener">BBC</a> ) <em>see also</em> <strong>How Trump&#39;s Election Lies Left the Michigan GOP Broken and Battered</strong> : Infighting between Trump acolytes and traditionalists has driven away donors and voters. Can the Michigan Republican Party rebuild in time for the presidential election? ( <a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2023/08/29/us/politics/trump-michigan-republican-party.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">New York Times</a> )</p><p> • <strong>Highways are the next antiabortion target. One Texas town is resisting</strong> . A new ordinance, passed in several jurisdictions and under consideration elsewhere, aims to stop people from using local roads to drive someone out of state for an abortion. ( <a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/politics/2023/09/01/texas-abortion-highways/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Washington Post</a> )</p></blockquote><p>请务必与 Jonathan Miller 一起观看本周的<a href="https://ritholtz.com/category/podcast/mib/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" data-web-url="http://www.bloombergview.com/topics/masters-in-business">商业硕士课程</a>，他是<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.millersamuel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Miller Samuel</a>的首席执行官，这是他于 1986 年共同创立的一家房地产评估和咨询公司。他是纽约州和康涅狄格州的州认证房地产评估师，擅长执行作为专家证人出庭作证，并拥有房地产顾问 (CRE) 和认证搬迁专业人士 (CRP) 称号。他的每周电子邮件<a class="gtrackexternal" href="https://www.millersamuel.com/email-lists/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">“住房笔记”</a>在评估和房地产经纪行业都被广泛阅读。米勒·塞缪尔 (Miller Samuel) 的研究和数据分析推动了许多全国房地产经纪出版物和战略计划的发展。</p><p></p><p> <strong>The Skyrocketing Toll of the Bil