 Row: Tycoons, High Rollers, and the Epic Race to Build the World&#39;s Most Exclusive Skyscrapers</a></strong> by Katherine Clark<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0593240065/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-319185" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brow.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="379" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brow.jpg 329w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brow-198x300.jpg 198w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/brow-250x379.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1419766392/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Easy Money: Cryptocurrency, Casino Capitalism, and the Golden Age of Fraud</a></strong> by Ben McKenzie with Jacob Silverman<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/1419766392/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-319186" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easymoney.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="377" srcset="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easymoney.jpg 331w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easymoney-199x300.jpg 199w, https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/easymoney-250x377.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 250px) 100vw, 250px" /></a></p><p> <strong><a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0063097206/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">The Slip: The New York City Street That Changed American Art Forever</a></strong> by Prudence Peiffer<br /> <a href="https://www.amazon.com/exec/obidos/ASIN/0063097206/thebigpictu09-20" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="alignnone wp-image-319187" src="https://ritholtz.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/theslip-1.jpg" alt="" width="250" height="377" srcset